dct_description_sm: Map of East Prussia, now part of Poland and Russia, to illustrate military tactics. Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. In upper margin: Zu: v. Alten, Kriegskunst in Aufgaben II. Map in German and English. From: Studies in applied tactics / by Lieutenant-General Georg von Alten : authorized translation (with substitution of American Army organization) by Major C. H. Barth. [Kansas City, Mo. : F.
